    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 9 (Spell Level 5)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 23 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 11 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 24</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique functions like Zankuusen. The maximum number of rays is 1 per 4 levels, and each ray deals 1d6+2 force damage. The knockback increases to 15 ft and the DC to avoid being stunned increases to 14. You may have the rays pass through any organic matter (including creatures) on their way to their intended target(s), though each creature they pass through will apply a cumulative -1 penalty to the attack roll for that ray attack.</p>\n\n\n\n",
